Package: pineconer
Type: Package
Title: R Interface to the Pinecone Vector Database
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Bob", "Rietveld",
                  email = "bob.rietveld@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a comprehensive R interface to the Pinecone Vector
    Database API. Supports index management (create, configure, delete),
    collection operations, and vector operations (query, upsert, fetch,
    update, delete). Uses the Pinecone Global API (api.pinecone.io)
    introduced in April 2024. Enables similarity search and retrieval
    augmented generation (RAG) workflows from R.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/bob-rietveld/pineconer
BugReports: https://github.com/bob-rietveld/pineconer/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
